name: PXL VZN Tatsu Adjaye x Casian Moore

metadata.name: Hack the Planet!
metadata.description: The Pixel Vision series features blockchain-born character, Tatsu Adjaye, living in a pixelated universe, vibin' to chill tunes, recalling retro hacker culture with a throwback to cult classic films, "War Games", "Hackers," and "Johnny Mnemonic". The music was composed by web3 rockstar, Casian Moore aka @Cas333.
